UID:9TqIrZyWMBkn2MmtlTF1_
SUMMARY:"Stop the Bleed" class
DTSTAMP:20260406T054324Z
DTSTART:20260414T020000Z
DESCRIPTION:Neighborhoods: Green Lake\,Greenwood/Phinney Ridge\,Ravenna/ Br
	yant/Roosevelt\n\nContact: Ann Forrest\, OEM Volunteer\n\nContact Email: O
	EM\\_StopTheBleed@Seattle.gov\n\nAudience: Adults\,Senior\,Special Nee ds\
	,Teen\n\nPre-Register: Yes\n\nCost: Free\n\nLink: https://www.seattle.gov/
	emergency-management/community-engagement/stop-the-bleed\n\nLife-threateni
	ng bleeding injuries can happen anytime. When they do\, every minute count
	s! Stop the Bleed empowers participants to take action! Our trained instru
	ctors teach the community about bleeding control: recognizing life-threate
	ning bleeding\, applying pressure to the wound\, and us ing a tourniquet.\
	n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/stop-the-bleed-class/1834
	7208/2026-04-13T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Community & Civic
URL:https://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/stop-the-bleed-class/1834
	7208/2026-04-13T00
LOCATION:Green Lake Community Center\, 7201 East Green Lake Dr N\, Seattle\
	, WA
